ee Benefits",description:"Benefits administration with carrier integrations and payroll deduction sync.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr/employee-benefits-software/"},{name:"Employee Equity",description:"Stock option and equity plan administration in 110+ countries with local tax compliance.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-services/employee-equity/"},{name:"Background Checks",description:"Employment screening in 190+ countries, integrated directly into the onboarding workflow.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-services/employee-background-checks/"},{name:"Employee Immigration",description:"Visa and work permit processing for employee relocations across countries.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-services/employee-immigration/"}]},{category:"IT",items:[{name:"Device Lifecycle Management",description:"Procure, ship, manage, and recover devices for employees in any country.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/device-lifecycle-management/"},{name:"Mobile Device Management",description:"Remote device configuration, updates, and security policies across operating systems.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/mobile-device-management/"},{name:"Endpoint Protection",description:"Threat monitoring and device security for distributed workforces.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/endpoint-protection/"},{name:"Identity & Access Management",description:"Automated app provisioning and de-provisioning tied to HR events.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/identity-access-management/"}]},{category:"Platform",items:[{name:"Deel AI",description:"AI assistant trained on Deel compliance and HR data across 150+ countries.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/ai/"},{name:"Compliance",description:"Automated contract generation, tax form collection, and local labor law compliance.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/compliance/"},{name:"Integrations",description:"Pre-built connectors for HRIS, accounting, ATS, and collaboration tools.",url:"https://www.deel.com/integrations/"},{name:"API",description:"REST API for synci